725
01:03:17,200 --> 01:03:20,540
而且 今早他上班前我还见过他 所以...
Plus I saw him this morning before he went to work, so...

726
01:03:22,910 --> 01:03:24,410
-给你 -谢谢
-Here. -Thanks.

727
01:03:24,500 --> 01:03:27,620
老实说 这件事太疯狂了
Honestly, this is... This is crazy.

728
01:03:29,910 --> 01:03:33,080
既然你这么担心你朋友 你应该报警
You should go to the police if you're so worried about your friend.

729
01:03:37,580 --> 01:03:39,080
他以前有没有出城
Does he ever go out of town

730
01:03:39,200 --> 01:03:41,410
-工作过？-没有
-for work or anything? -No.

731
01:03:41,500 --> 01:03:45,120
他们一周前去了卡蒂奇格罗夫
Well, they went away to Cottage Grove, like, a week ago,

732
01:03:45,200 --> 01:03:49,000
从那以后我就再也没有她的消息了 我只是...
and I haven't heard from her since then and I'm just...

733
01:03:49,080 --> 01:03:50,700
我不知道那在哪里
I don't know where that is.

734
01:03:53,450 --> 01:03:55,870
-我只是很担心 好吗？-我明白
-I'm just worried, okay? -Yeah, I understand.

735
01:03:57,660 --> 01:03:59,040
我真的很抱歉
I'm really sorry.

736
01:04:01,500 --> 01:04:04,870
我丈夫回来了 你得走了
That's my husband right now. You need to leave, okay?

737
01:04:04,950 --> 01:04:07,080
我只是走投无路了 咱们女人之间说一句
I'm just desperate. Woman-to-woman,

738
01:04:07,080 --> 01:04:08,870
也许你丈夫知道更多信息
maybe your husband has more information.

739
01:04:08,950 --> 01:04:11,160
我不是来找事的
I'm not trying to mess anything up for anybody here.

740
01:04:11,250 --> 01:04:12,250
-嗨 -我只是想找到我的朋友
I'm just trying to find my friend.

741
01:04:15,200 --> 01:04:16,910
-你好 嗨 -嘿
-Hello. Hi. -Hey.

742
01:04:21,290 --> 01:04:23,370
-这是怎么回事？-没什么
-What's going on? -Nothing.

743
01:04:23,450 --> 01:04:25,450
没什么 这个女人正要走
Nothing. This woman was just leaving.

744
01:04:26,450 --> 01:04:29,200
-你是史蒂夫 对吧？-不 我是布兰登
- You're Steve, right? - No, I'm Brendan.

745
01:04:29,450 --> 01:04:31,370
但别人都叫你史蒂夫 对吧？
But you go by Steve, right?

746
01:04:32,000 --> 01:04:35,330
不是 就是布兰登 你是谁？
No. Just Brendan. Who are you?

747
01:04:36,290 --> 01:04:38,000
我是莫莉
I'm Mollie. Um...

748
01:04:38,080 --> 01:04:42,450
我的朋友诺亚 我想你认识她 她失踪了
My friend Noa, uh, I think you know her, she's missing.

749
01:04:42,910 --> 01:04:47,330
诺亚 抱歉 我不认识
Noa. Um... No, I'm sorry, I... I don't.

750
01:04:48,870 --> 01:04:50,910
-你认识吗 亲爱的？-当然不认识
-Do you, honey? -No, of course not.

751
01:04:51,410 --> 01:04:55,580
太可怕了 我不知道 我想你找错房子了
That's terrible. Yeah, I don't know, I think you have the wrong house.

752
01:04:58,700 --> 01:05:01,830
是啊 你也许是对的
Yeah. Yeah, you're probably right.

753
01:05:03,250 --> 01:05:06,700
-好吧 抱歉打扰了 -没事
-Okay. -I'm sorry. Sorry about that. -No.

754
01:05:06,790 --> 01:05:08,120
很遗憾我们帮不上忙
We're sorry we couldn't help you.

755
01:05:08,120 --> 01:05:09,660
我们很同情你朋友的遭遇
Sorry about your friend.

756
01:05:13,620 --> 01:05:16,200
你最后一次见她是什么时候？
I'm just thinking, when's the last time you saw her?

757
01:05:16,330 --> 01:05:17,200
诺亚

758
01:05:26,160 --> 01:05:27,450
是你
Oh, it's you.

759
01:05:28,450 --> 01:05:30,540
莫莉 对吧？
Mollie, right?

760
01:05:32,370 --> 01:05:33,450
你真不该多此一举
Really shouldn't have done that.

761
01:05:47,040 --> 01:05:50,370
发生了什么事？

762
01:05:58,330 --> 01:05:59,500
诺亚说我们会合得来
Noa said we'd get along.

763
01:05:59,580 --> 01:06:00,580
该死的
Fuck!

764
01:06:05,620 --> 01:06:06,620
让我们检验下
Let's see.

765
01:06:13,950 --> 01:06:18,620
你为什么问我人肉的味道？
So... why did you ask me what it tasted like?

766
01:06:24,290 --> 01:06:25,370
我不知道
I don't know.

767
01:06:28,120 --> 01:06:31,120
我想我只是好奇
I guess I was... curious.

768
01:06:32,700 --> 01:06:34,200
你好奇？
You were curious?

769
01:06:35,870 --> 01:06:37,410
你觉得我会相信吗？
You expect me to believe that?

770
01:06:40,000 --> 01:06:41,830
信不信随你
You can believe what you want.

771
01:06:47,660 --> 01:06:48,660
好吧
Okay.

772
01:06:54,950 --> 01:06:57,500
我们一起吃晚饭 看看你有多好奇
Let's have dinner and we'll see how curious you are.

773
01:06:58,790 --> 01:07:00,000
我给你带来了一些衣服
Brought you some stuff.

774
01:07:01,080 --> 01:07:04,410
我猜你可能想换个打扮
Figured you might wanna... change.

775
01:07:33,580 --> 01:07:35,080
拜托 你在哪？

776
01:07:36,000 --> 01:07:36,830
莫莉的位置

777
01:07:38,790 --> 01:07:40,000
该死
Fuck.

778
01:08:30,450 --> 01:08:32,660
孩子们都睡了吗？
The boys go down okay?

779
01:08:33,200 --> 01:08:35,790
他们要找你
They asked for you.

780
01:08:49,370 --> 01:08:51,700
-工作怎么样？-挺好
How was work? -Good.

781
01:08:52,250 --> 01:08:55,160
明天我会晚点回来
Actually, I'm gonna be late tomorrow night.

782
01:08:56,200 --> 01:08:58,370
因为新产品的关系 有很多工作要做
Lots to do now with the new product.

783
01:08:58,750 --> 01:09:01,290
一些大客户等着收货呢
Got some big clients expecting deliveries.

784
01:09:16,330 --> 01:09:19,540
-我要洗个澡 -今天合作愉快
- I'm gonna take a shower. -Good teamwork today.

785
01:11:58,120 --> 01:11:59,580
姓名:约翰逊 日期:4月1日

786
01:11:59,660 --> 01:12:02,910
姓名:阮 日期:1月20日

787
01:13:00,330 --> 01:13:04,120
放心 我不会给你下药的 不会干第二次
Don't worry, I'm not gonna drug you. Again.

788
01:13:05,370 --> 01:13:06,830
你最好不要
You better not.

789
01:13:10,450 --> 01:13:11,450
干杯
Cheers.

790
01:13:14,200 --> 01:13:15,200
干杯
Cheers.

791
01:13:22,870 --> 01:13:24,750
你之前提到你很好奇
So you mentioned you were curious.

792
01:13:27,330 --> 01:13:31,450
-对 -好吧 你想知道什么？
-Yeah. -All right, what do you wanna know?

793
01:13:34,160 --> 01:13:38,330
嗯...
Well... Um...

794
01:13:40,700 --> 01:13:42,580
你第一次尝试是什么时候？
When did you first try it?

795
01:13:44,250 --> 01:13:47,620
我当时18或19岁
I was, um, 18 or 19.

796
01:13:48,790 --> 01:13:51,830
19岁 对 而且你看
Nineteen, yeah. And, look...

797
01:13:53,120 --> 01:13:54,830
这不是我一时兴起
it wasn't an overnight thing, you know?

798
01:13:55,870 --> 01:13:57,330
一开始我真的很害怕
First, I was actually horrified.

799
01:13:57,410 --> 01:14:01,200
我怎么能做出这种事？
I mean, how could possibly be capable of doing something like this?

800
01:14:01,290 --> 01:14:05,500
我是个正常孩子 我有朋友 过着正常的生活
You know, I was a normal kid, I had friends, I had a normal life,

801
01:14:06,660 --> 01:14:09,290
现在我得面对这些
and now I gotta deal with this thing

802
01:14:09,830 --> 01:14:12,580
我无法与任何人分享
that I couldn't share with anybody.

803
01:14:12,700 --> 01:14:16,790
这让我饱受煎熬 但我总是忍不住去想
And that killed me. But I couldn't stop thinking about it.

804
01:14:17,620 --> 01:14:21,120
我无法舍弃对人肉的迷恋
I couldn't get the, um, taste out of my mouth.

805
01:14:21,790 --> 01:14:23,000
那种质感
The texture.

806
01:14:24,120 --> 01:14:27,660
我很喜欢 我喜欢那种唇齿间的滋味
I liked it. I liked the way it made me feel.

807
01:14:28,620 --> 01:14:29,660
所以我想
So I thought,

808
01:14:29,660 --> 01:14:31,750
“我必须找出 是否还有更多跟我一样的人”
"I gotta find out if there's more out there," you know.

809
01:14:31,870 --> 01:14:35,000
“我不可能是唯一有这种癖好的人”
"I can't possibly be the only person that feels this way."

810
01:14:35,500 --> 01:14:37,160
事实证明 我确实不是
And I wasn't.

811
01:14:38,080 --> 01:14:41,080
有一整群人都沉迷于此
There's a whole community of people that are devoted to this.

812
01:14:42,950 --> 01:14:47,410
就在那一刻 我的人生开始变得有意义
And that's when my life started making sense.

813
01:14:49,330 --> 01:14:54,160
我是说 那是一个非常强大的组织
I mean, it's... It's a very powerful thing.

814
01:14:55,700 --> 01:14:58,410
这整个世界 如果你知道的话
This whole world, if you only knew. It's, um...

815
01:15:01,160 --> 01:15:02,580
生命的意义在于奉献
It's about giving.

816
01:15:04,660 --> 01:15:07,700
把自己交给别人
Giving yourself over to somebody.

817
01:15:09,160 --> 01:15:12,580
永远与他人合而为一
Becoming one with somebody else, forever.

818
01:15:13,950 --> 01:15:18,540
那是非常美妙的事
And that's... That's a beautiful thing.

819
01:15:20,950 --> 01:15:22,250
那是臣服
That's surrender.

820
01:15:23,870 --> 01:15:25,000
那是爱
That's love.

821
01:15:33,410 --> 01:15:35,830
这个组织里有多少人？
And how many people are in this community?

822
01:15:36,540 --> 01:15:37,620
不多
Not many.

823
01:15:39,290 --> 01:15:41,080
最富有的1%人群中的1%
The one percent of the one percent.

824
01:15:42,290 --> 01:15:45,200
没有什么是这些人买不起的 对吧？
You know, there's nothing these people can't afford, right?

825
01:15:45,290 --> 01:15:49,450
他们想要的是别人没有的
They want the one thing that no one else has

826
01:15:50,250 --> 01:15:51,580
或者得不到的
or can get.

827
01:15:52,790 --> 01:15:54,660
我填补了这个空白
And that's where I come in.

828
01:15:56,580 --> 01:15:58,000
我可以给他们供货
I can get it for them.

829
01:16:00,540 --> 01:16:02,660
我因此在圈子里出了名
I made a name for myself.

830
01:16:06,040 --> 01:16:07,870
你们只吃女人吗？
Is it only women that you eat?

831
01:16:09,790 --> 01:16:13,370
-对 -为什么？
-Yeah. -Why?

832
01:16:14,080 --> 01:16:19,080
这是市场的需求 另外 女人的味道更好
That's where the market is. Plus, women just taste better.

833
01:16:21,120 --> 01:16:22,120
所以...
So...

834
01:16:25,120 --> 01:16:27,080
我准备了一道菜肴
I cooked us something.

835
01:16:28,500 --> 01:16:30,200
如果你愿意尝试的话
If you're open to trying it.

836
01:16:36,000 --> 01:16:37,120
这是...
Is it...

837
01:16:39,290 --> 01:16:40,410
这是我的肉吗？
Is it me?

838
01:16:43,120 --> 01:16:44,160
不是
No.

839
01:16:46,700 --> 01:16:48,540
我们一起吃
We'll have a bite together.

840
01:17:45,040 --> 01:17:47,450
这顿饭价值三万美元
This meal is about $30,000.

841
01:17:49,540 --> 01:17:53,580
-太疯狂了 -如果她还活着 价格更高
-That's crazy. -Be a lot more if she was still alive.

842
01:17:54,450 --> 01:17:55,450
希望
Hope.

843
01:17:57,120 --> 01:17:58,290
那是她的名字
That was her name.

844
01:17:59,870 --> 01:18:00,870
有点好笑
Kinda funny.

845
01:18:02,540 --> 01:18:06,040
是有点好笑 太蠢了
It's kinda funny. Stupid.

846
01:18:10,200 --> 01:18:12,120
跟我想象中不太一样
It's not what I expected.

847
01:18:14,790 --> 01:18:15,790
这味道
It's, um...

848
01:18:18,290 --> 01:18:20,000
难以形容
It's indescribable.

849
01:18:45,500 --> 01:18:49,830
-谢谢你 史蒂夫 -不客气 诺亚
-Thank you, Steve. -You're welcome, Noa.

850
01:18:54,410 --> 01:18:56,370
你知道我怎么晓得你很特别吗？
You know how I knew you were special?

851
01:18:59,910 --> 01:19:01,620
因为你跟我一样都不正常
'Cause you're fucked up, too.

852
01:19:52,450 --> 01:19:54,160
我们走吧
All right. Let's go.

853
01:20:31,290 --> 01:20:32,290
诺亚
Noa!

854
01:20:35,580 --> 01:20:36,790
佩妮 是你吗？
Penny. Yeah?

855
01:20:37,450 --> 01:20:40,910
肯定不是梅丽莎
That definitely didn't sound like Melissa.

856
01:20:42,580 --> 01:20:46,080
是啊 听起来像新人
Yeah. Sounds like someone new.

857
01:20:56,160 --> 01:20:58,950
前几天晚上
You know, the other night,

858
01:20:59,790 --> 01:21:05,080
我在想 跟你聊天
I was thinking about how nice

859
01:21:05,660 --> 01:21:07,660
有多开心
it's been to talk to you.

860
01:21:09,580 --> 01:21:13,580
但后来我想 有没有可能你不是真的
But then I was like, what if you're not real...

861
01:21:13,580 --> 01:21:15,250
莫莉的位置不可用

862
01:21:15,290 --> 01:21:19,500
是我自己疯了？
and I'm just going crazy?

863
01:21:21,660 --> 01:21:23,160
像梅丽莎那样
Like Melissa.

864
01:21:25,950 --> 01:21:31,410
但我想如果自己有一个想象中的朋友
But I feel like if I had an imaginary friend,

865
01:21:33,080 --> 01:21:35,080
我不会给她起名叫诺亚
I wouldn't name her Noa.

866
01:21:36,580 --> 01:21:40,580
我会叫她肖恩·康纳利
It'd be, like... Sean Connery.

867
01:21:54,200 --> 01:21:56,080
真希望能见到你
I wish I could see you.

868
01:22:04,250 --> 01:22:05,580
我也是
Me, too.

869
01:22:14,790 --> 01:22:16,290
我有东西给你
I have something for you.

870
01:22:19,410 --> 01:22:22,700
来吧 打开它
Go ahead. Open it.

871
01:22:48,580 --> 01:22:50,000
你喜欢吗？
Do you like it?

872
01:22:54,200 --> 01:22:56,450
是粉色的
It's pink.

873
01:22:58,370 --> 01:22:59,830
我很喜欢
I love it.

874
01:23:00,870 --> 01:23:01,870
谢谢
Thank you.

875
01:23:02,500 --> 01:23:05,290
也许你可以今晚穿上
Maybe you can wear it tonight and,

876
01:23:06,330 --> 01:23:08,160
我们可以再次一起吃晚饭
we can have dinner again.

877
01:23:10,330 --> 01:23:11,950
好啊
Yeah. Okay.

878
01:23:15,620 --> 01:23:17,160
我7点来接你
I'll pick you up at 7:00.

879
01:23:19,500 --> 01:23:22,080
-我对时间已经没有概念了 -我知道
-I have no idea what time it is. -I know.

880
01:23:23,790 --> 01:23:24,790
当然
Sure.

881
01:23:34,950 --> 01:23:36,580
也许你可以梳洗打扮一下
Maybe you can freshen up.

882
01:24:35,120 --> 01:24:37,330
安 你什么时候回家？

883
01:25:12,950 --> 01:25:16,290
你好 嗨
Well, hello. Hi.

884
01:25:31,120 --> 01:25:33,700
看来我们已经进展到正经约会了
I see we've made it to the dinner table.

885
01:25:33,790 --> 01:25:36,290
是的
Yes, we have.

886
01:25:39,450 --> 01:25:43,250
这是约会吗 史蒂夫？
Is, um...? Is this a date, Steve?

887
01:25:46,830 --> 01:25:48,040
也许是吧
Maybe it is.

888
01:26:09,000 --> 01:26:12,700
嗯...好吧
Well... All right.

889
01:26:14,160 --> 01:26:16,160
这将是一个有趣的夜晚
It's gonna be an interesting night.

890
01:26:16,450 --> 01:26:20,500
-是啊 确实 -好极了
- Yeah. It is. - Great.

891
01:26:22,450 --> 01:26:23,750
让我们大醉一场
Let's get drunk.

892
01:26:25,000 --> 01:26:27,120
我在想你那天晚上说的话
I was thinking about what you said that night.

893
01:26:27,200 --> 01:26:29,250
关于独自长大
About growing up alone and all.

894
01:26:30,700 --> 01:26:35,620
让我意识到没有人真正为你做过饭
Made me realize nobody's ever really cooked for you.

895
01:26:36,910 --> 01:26:38,250
这让我很难过
And that made me sad.

896
01:26:40,450 --> 01:26:43,660
每个人都必须有人为他们做一次饭
Everyone has to have someone cook for them once.

897
01:26:45,200 --> 01:26:46,200
肉酱
Pate.

898
01:26:46,750 --> 01:26:50,500
-肝脏 -还有大蒜和迷迭香
- Liver. - And garlic and rosemary.

899
01:27:03,540 --> 01:27:07,950
我确实吃出了大蒜的味道
I do taste the garlic. Definitely.

900
01:27:08,080 --> 01:27:11,450
你可以下次做 以你喜欢的方式
You can make it next time. Just the way you like it.

901
01:27:18,450 --> 01:27:19,790
这是谁？
Who's this?

902
01:27:22,080 --> 01:27:23,950
这个？
This?

903
01:27:27,620 --> 01:27:28,950
这是梅丽莎
This is Melissa.

904
01:27:35,500 --> 01:27:36,660
梅丽莎
Melissa.

905
01:27:44,120 --> 01:27:47,870
这名字太普通了 不是吗？
I mean, that's so boring. Isn't it?

906
01:27:48,830 --> 01:27:50,000
就好像她...
Like, she...

907
01:27:52,120 --> 01:27:57,700
她的肉尝起来有滋有味 而她竟然叫梅丽莎
She tastes so, you know, decadent... and her name's Melissa.

908
01:27:58,250 --> 01:27:59,250
好吧...
Well...

909
01:28:00,870 --> 01:28:05,790
我以为你会说“愉悦”
Thought you were gonna say something, you know, like, Joy.

910
01:28:08,910 --> 01:28:13,370
-看来希望都被吃光了 -没有 希望还剩下很多
